### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">فَلَمَّا ٱعْتَزَلَهُمْ وَمَا يَعْبُدُونَ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ وَهَبْنَا لَهُۥٓ إِسْحَـٰقَ وَيَعْقُوبَ ۖ وَكُلًّا جَعَلْنَا نَبِيًّا</span>

### English

So after he had left them and what they worshipped besides Allah, We granted him Isaac and Jacob, and made each of them a prophet.